412
00:30:18,820 --> 00:30:24,170
So we'll live on that desert island together until we die.

413
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:29,720
You remember, right?

414
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:32,920
Yeah.

415
00:30:34,100 --> 00:30:37,100
Ha Na, what's up with you?

416
00:30:37,100 --> 00:30:38,900
Did something happen with Ho Joon?

417
00:30:38,900 --> 00:30:41,180
This is all...

418
00:30:42,700 --> 00:30:44,100
Because of you.

419
00:30:44,100 --> 00:30:47,540
