No way!

425
00:31:09,330 --> 00:31:12,460
The rumor is spread everywhere at school that Won likes you.

426
00:31:12,460 --> 00:31:14,440
He buys toast for you all the time too.

427
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:17,260
Wow, really. Does buying toast for me mean he likes me?

428
00:31:17,260 --> 00:31:22,620
That... He isn't buying it for me randomly. He lost a bet, so he's doing it.

429
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:27,750
But why are you guys going around together all the time?

430
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:33,800
Since we were younger, we lived in the same neighborhood and also went to the same school,

431
00:31:33,800 --> 00:31:36,800
