438
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:03,900
But I was worried you also like him.

439
00:32:05,800 --> 00:32:07,690
I'm speechless, really.

440
00:32:07,690 --> 00:32:10,750
Hey! What style of girls does Won like?

441
00:32:10,750 --> 00:32:13,320
Well... I don't know.

442
00:32:13,320 --> 00:32:16,100
Do you think he'd match well with me?

443
00:32:17,090 --> 00:32:18,260
A little?

444
00:32:18,260 --> 00:32:21,080
Hey! Then you better push us together now! Got it?

445
00:32:21,080 --> 00:32:23,800
Fine! What's the big deal?

446
00:32:23,800 --> 00:32:26,210
How should I push you?

447
00:32:26,210 --> 00:32:29,150
Give this to him.

448
00:32:29,150 --> 00:32:34,740
- You give it to him.
- Let me test him out first. What if I suddenly go for him, and then he says he doesn't like me?

449
00:32:34,740 --> 00:32:37,020
Come on.

450
00:32:37,020 --> 00:32:39,770
Ugh, really.

