00:35:01,950 --> 00:35:06,370
Just take it for now. You'll know if you accept  it.

463
00:35:06,370 --> 00:35:10,090
This... Who do you think gave it to you?

464
00:35:10,090 --> 00:35:13,690
- Me or...
