471
00:35:37,530 --> 00:35:40,250
After opening my eyes, I see everyone else is dead.

472
00:35:40,250 --> 00:35:43,690
Only you and I are alive. Just the two of us.

473
00:35:45,250 --> 00:35:51,350
So we live on that uninhabited island until we die.

474
00:35:54,250 --> 00:35:56,930
But still, I will never date you.

475
00:35:58,210 --> 00:36:00,310
