476
00:36:00,310 --> 00:36:04,810
Even if we were to fall onto a desert island, I will never love you.

477
00:36:04,810 --> 00:36:06,790
For my entire life.

478
00:36:12,070 --> 00:36:14,350
Ah, is that so?

479
00:36:15,430 --> 00:36:17,510
That's a relief.

480
00:36:19,150 --> 00:36:21,610
That's a relief,

481
00:36:23,110 --> 00:36:25,770
