484
00:36:50,750 --> 00:36:53,990
Hey, Choi Won! I don't like you either!

485
00:36:53,990 --> 00:36:56,210
Forget uninhabited island, but even the North Pole, the South Pole, a desert or the sea!

486
00:36:56,210 --> 00:37:00,310
Even if I fall into the sea, I won't date you! I'm telling you I won't!

487
00:37:00,310 --> 00:37:04,910
And this, this is from Na Yeong, not me!

488
00:37:05,910 --> 00:37:08,390
